                negates the debate proposition. The default argument type is"FOR"
                meaning the following argument supports the debate proposition. Since
                this is your own proposition, I hope that your arguments are supporting
                it. But in all fairness, you might choose to enter standard arguments
                against the proposition in order to dispatch them in counter-arguments.</p>
            </li>
